  9  /-!
 10  # Algebraic elements and algebraic extensions
 11  
 12  An element of an R-algebra is algebraic over R if it is the root of a nonzero polynomial.
 13  An R-algebra is algebraic over R if and only if all its elements are algebraic over R.
 14  The main result in this file proves transitivity of algebraicity:
 15  a tower of algebraic field extensions is algebraic.
 16  -/
 17  
 18  universe variables u v
